2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of the expectation-maximization algorithm, which is a common machine learning algorithm. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the algorithmic feasibility of community detection in higher-order networks, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses the implementation of the expectation-maximization algorithm with belief propagation, which is a topic related to software engineering. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - Although not directly related to neural or evolutionary computing, the paper discusses the use of algorithms to detect modular structures in networks, which is a topic related to computational intelligence.
